*"Zašto* si me izneo?" (Why did you betray me?)

*"Šta* je razlog *zašto* si otišao?" (What was the reason why you left?)

*"Kako* se postaviti *zašto* bih otišao?" (How should I position myself so that I would leave?)

*"Ne znam* *zašto* se ovo desilo." (I don't know why this happened.)

*"Da li* je to razlog *zašto* ne možeš da dođeš?" (Is that the reason why you can't come?)

*"Koliko* je puta ti si pitao *zašto*?" (How many times have you asked why?)